UI Health                     Search the site     Toggle Menu      Search              UI Health                     UI Health   Main Menu    About Us           We are UI Health         Health Colleges    Healthcare    Research & Clinical Trials    Community     Eyebrow menu    MAKE A GIFT    UIC menu    UI Health    UIC.edu    Campus Map       Search                         Health Sciences Colleges at UIC      View Menu            Educating Healthcare Leaders of the Future  In addition to providing high-quality patient care to communities and neighborhoods across the state of Illinois, the academic health enterprise of UI Health incorporates the educational functions of UIC's seven health sciences colleges to better prepare students for future careers in healthcare.  Representing the seven health sciences colleges and their numerous programs and specialties, UI Health has trained thousands of healthcare professionals who practice around the city of Chicago, across the state of Illinois and throughout the United StatesÂ  - and beyond.
